Get Docker "virtual container" (Windows download)
https://github.com/docker/toolbox/releases/download/v1.9.1i/DockerToolbox-1.9.1i.exe
Get Started with Docker for Windows: https://docs.docker.com/windows/

Activity Streams store
Open Ahjo API -> Local Mongo DB (server.js)
https://github.com/samuelmr/activitystore-poc
Get the 10 most recent objects: http://localhost:5000/object/?max=10

Reads agenda items from Helsinki Decisions API, transforms the items into Activity Streams and pushes the events into activitystreams-server.
(Python)
https://github.com/okffi/decision-streamer

Reference implementation of an ActivityStreams 2.0 server
We use Grunt, npm, and mongodb. Mongo needs to be running for ActivityStreams 2.0 server to work.
https://github.com/OpenSocial/activitystreams-server

A D-CENT project: A simple service for storing, retrieving and signing activities (Activity Stream 2.0)
https://github.com/d-cent/coracle

How to start
https://hub.docker.com/_/mongo/
docker run --name some-mongo -d mongo
docker pull dcent/coracle
docker run -d --name coracle --link mongo:mongo -p 7000:7000 dcent/coracle

UI:
https://github.com/ThoughtWorksInc/helsinki
